Usage: setLimitedAccessFeature [-help] <featureName> <1 | 0>

-help             # Prints out the command usage
<featureName>     # Specifies the name of the limited access feature.
                  # (string, required)
<1 | 0>           # Specifying the value 1 enables the feature.Specifying the
                  # value 0 disables the feature. (bool, required)